-- Lucara Diamond to Commission Botswana Mine, CEO Says
-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 2012-02-09T06:04:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-09/lucara-diamond-to-commission-botswana-mine-ceo-says-correct-.html
(Corrects to say mine to be commissioned 18 months after
feasibility study in story published yesterday.)  Lucara Diamond Corp. plans to
commission its Karowe mine in Botswana in April, 18 months after
completing a feasibility study, Chief Executive Officer William
Lamb said in a presentation at the Investing in African Mining
Indaba conference in  Cape Town  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  